title: Brain.Trainer.1&2-ViTALiTY
description:
Packed from 1.4GB to 37MB! have fun!

Brain Trainer (c) Mindscape
Have fun raising the fitness  of  your  brain  to  perform
better at everyday tasks. Play a daily range of activities
in the 10 minute "Daily Brain Training"  and  review  your
progress, or just play your choice of activities  for  the
challenge.  Mindscape&#039;s  Brain  Training  software,   with
unlimited questions and engaging exercises,  is  the  only
Brain Food you&#039;ll need on your PC!

Brain Trainer 2 (c) Mindscape
Train your brain even better with Brainer Trainer 2.  This
cd-rom includes more  exercises  to  enhanc  your  memory.
Become  smarter  by  "mind  enhancing"  activities,   like
spelling test, word search, colour tiles,  Domino,  colour
matching, number sequence and  more.  Play  Brain  Trainer
every day and check  your  statistics  for  your  personal
development.
